addition(/subtraction use minus everywhere):
*0/n + 0/m = 0
*0/n + i/m = i/m
*i/n + j/n = i+j/n
*reduce
i/n + j/m = (i*m) + (j*n)/(n*m)
5/10 + 10/10 = 15/10 = 3/2
2/5 + 2/10 = 3/5

multiplication:
0/n * 0/m = 0
i/n * m/m = i/n
i/n * j/n = i*j/n
i/n * j/m = (i*m) * (j*n) / (n*m)
5/10 * 10/10 = 150/10 = 15/1
2/5 * 2/10 = 4/5

division:
0/n / 0/m = exception
i/n / m/m = i/n
i/n / j/n = i/n * n/j = i/j
i/n / j/m = (i/n) * (m/j) = (i*j) / (m*n)
5/10 * 10/10 = 150/10 = 15/1
2/5 * 2/10 = 4/5

